{"tid":1745232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【光復連登】只需簡單三步 驅逐五毛熱狗風向分化撚","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T10:03:37.000Z","uid":226773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5db64089b1177ecd9e9fa83ed8c7220a76438f7e","tid":1745232,"uid":226773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:18:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">第一步   封鎖名單與追蹤名單</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n-首先檢查一下自己的追蹤名單有沒有追蹤不必要用戶<br />\n<br />\n-如果可行請盡量清空追蹤名單<br />\n<br />\n-若未能清空，請記下剩餘帳戶(如#號)以免拉錯清白用戶<br />\n<br />\n-你若有封鎖五毛的習慣，建議你把你封鎖名單中的所有用戶轉為追蹤<br />\n<br />\n-請持續地追蹤五毛<br />\n<br />\n-善用起底功能以避免誤會及網絡欺凌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">第二步   出post時不推文拉</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n-按左邊功能列，你能見到「追蹤中」，此功能可讓你方便快捷的看到需要拉的post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-連登有一項留言功能叫不推文回覆，請善用<br />\n<br />\n-若是沒有惡意的post，可以不拉同時呼籲其他用戶追蹤(下一步說明原因)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">第三步   提醒他人</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n-若發現有五毛企圖帶風向或分化，可以留言提醒大家防範以及追蹤五毛的重要性<br />\n<br />\n-越多人追蹤五毛及進行以上步驟，五毛的影響力將越少"},{"pid":"1c3ceacfac197fbc62b23f6d90dd3e4ff170b7f3","tid":1745232,"uid":226773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3354453eb8a19c1e7217acade31a55143e1662d7","tid":1745232,"uid":226773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:19:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3153397bfdf1ca9e64a843a772d4d216b76e4de","tid":1745232,"uid":226773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:19:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19da85ce351d50d72c6a3f47f12a27a6360902df","tid":1745232,"uid":226773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:19:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8018d366184b909486cf455429466ac097ef770","tid":1745232,"uid":226773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB